{"tid":869799,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Google Pixel 出現影相 Bug 拍攝後照片離奇消失","createTime":"2018-10-20T14:26:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T16:18:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f2c9a32fa0866f0b23fa854d456ceb1e6f419b71","tid":869799,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T14:26:05.000Z","msg":"藍骨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGoogle 自家 Pixel 系列雖然一向以最強拍攝功能見稱，但最近在 Pixel 3 系列推出之後，有部分用家遇到了攝影 Bug，在拍攝之後照片會無法開啓，消失不見。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在 Reddit 上，有一些 Pixel 用家表示，在透過 Google Camera 拍攝後如果切換到其他 App 或者鎖機，之後雖然可以看到照片的縮圖，但點擊之後就會消失，無法開啓。有些情況下這些照片會在一日之後再次出現。問題除了在新的 Pixel 3 系列手機上出現，舊款的 Pixel 和 Pixel 2 系列據稱也有這個問題發生。 <br />\n<br />\n除了 Pixel 外，一部分 Galaxy S9、Moto Z2、Moto E4 和 Nexus 5X 用家也報告指使用 Google Camera 時出現類似問題，因此暫時仍然未知這是 Pixel 的問題還是 Android 的問題。有用家估計是 HDR 運算出現問題，關閉 HDR 的話可以避免問題發生。暫時 Google 方面未有回應問題，相信仍然有待進一步研究。"},{"pid":"9ae074c7c82854c280dba623c839037d380e7598","tid":869799,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T14:38:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/10/20/google-pixel-2-3-camera-photos-saving-bug/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2Fgoogle-pixel-2-3-camera-photos-saving-bug%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=615rysS2UWjGrm1Hpz%2F2dpUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=11e9b13e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/10/20/google-pixel-2-3-camera-photos-saving-bug/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"1519c7f4f74f4a87288cd386f86f80bcd626c688","tid":869799,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T14:59:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f598ea1c6b8dc25bf492870fb0943efcaacacb3e","tid":869799,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T15:03:52.000Z","msg":"又開係時事台囉，開慣左手勢都要識改下架"},{"pid":"e35175c3cb48cae427cda2aae828cd17843cf7a5","tid":869799,"uid":22675,"like":0,"disli